591
00:26:20,310 --> 00:26:21,530
Yes.

592
00:26:24,160 --> 00:26:26,330
You were introduced by Mr. Li?

593
00:26:26,400 --> 00:26:27,470
Yes.

594
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:29,220
I mean...

595
00:26:30,160 --> 00:26:32,180
