596
00:26:32,460 --> 00:26:33,680
You invest a portion too,

597
00:26:33,680 --> 00:26:35,010
and we can work together

598
00:26:35,090 --> 00:26:36,330
to make a good movie.

599
00:26:36,510 --> 00:26:36,980
Yes.

600
00:26:37,180 --> 00:26:38,180
Even if we lose,

601
00:26:38,180 --> 00:26:39,640
