612
00:26:55,020 --> 00:26:55,950
Absolutely not.

613
00:26:57,610 --> 00:26:58,670
Just kidding.

614
00:27:01,330 --> 00:27:02,990
Mr. Sui, how about this?

615
00:27:03,350 --> 00:27:04,660
