620
00:27:12,530 --> 00:27:14,130
It's actually quite simple.

621
00:27:14,500 --> 00:27:16,330
You can just get a bank loan.

622
00:27:17,240 --> 00:27:19,310
Individuals and businesses

623
00:27:19,330 --> 00:27:20,330
