624
00:27:20,810 --> 00:27:22,220
As long as you have collateral.

625
00:27:22,220 --> 00:27:23,400
The procedures are very simple.

626
00:27:23,400 --> 00:27:25,240
The interest rate is also very reasonable.

627
00:27:25,240 --> 00:27:25,770
However,

628
00:27:26,460 --> 00:27:27,070
