to my company's account.

633
00:27:33,110 --> 00:27:34,840
It's easier to manage that way.

634
00:27:35,090 --> 00:27:37,220
I really don't know anything
about making movies.

635
00:27:37,220 --> 00:27:37,720
See?

636
00:27:38,160 --> 00:27:40,000
This golf course is mine.

637
00:27:40,850 --> 00:27:41,270
When the time comes,

638
00:27:41,270 --> 00:27:42,460
