640
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:44,810
Film whatever you want.

641
00:27:44,810 --> 00:27:45,740
You can use the money

642
00:27:45,740 --> 00:27:46,590
however you want.

643
00:27:46,590 --> 00:27:47,920
I'll fully support you.

644
00:27:48,700 --> 00:27:49,630
Just one thing—

645
00:27:49,830 --> 00:27:51,160
what I need is not money,

646
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:54,290
but sincerity and confidence.

647
00:27:55,290 --> 00:27:55,940
In short,

648
00:27:56,680 --> 00:27:57,530
integrity.

649
00:27:59,510 --> 00:28:01,510
Alright, I'll take a few more putts.

650
00:28:01,590 --> 00:28:02,250
Okay, okay.

651
00:28:02,310 --> 00:28:02,970
Okay, okay.

652
00:28:12,660 --> 00:28:13,520
Director Weng.

653
00:28:14,270 --> 00:28:15,870
I really want to give it a try.

654
00:28:17,160 --> 00:28:20,700
You decided to get a personal loan?

655
00:28:22,850 --> 00:28:23,400
Well...

656
00:28:24,180 --> 00:28:25,330
Hasn't Mr. Sui

657
00:28:25,350 --> 00:28:25,900
