670
00:28:45,810 --> 00:28:46,200
Yeah.

671
00:28:47,900 --> 00:28:50,030
But do you have any assets to mortgage?

672
00:28:53,680 --> 00:28:54,420
N-No.

673
00:28:57,250 --> 00:28:57,780
Alright.

674
00:28:58,530 --> 00:29:00,720
I really appreciate you as a person,

675
