693
00:29:32,770 --> 00:29:33,230
Come on!

694
00:29:43,530 --> 00:29:45,590
I'm sure this movie will be a success.

695
00:29:45,850 --> 00:29:48,140
That spirit of fighting for your dreams

696
00:29:48,180 --> 00:29:49,810
