715
00:30:22,180 --> 00:30:22,580
Right!

716
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:25,460
Are you laughing at me?

717
00:30:25,460 --> 00:30:26,140
Are you making fun of me?

718
00:30:26,140 --> 00:30:27,420
No, I'm not.

719
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:28,500
It's just that...

720
00:30:28,500 --> 00:30:29,660
listening to you speak just now,

721
00:30:29,660 --> 00:30:30,790
I suddenly felt like

722
00:30:31,240 --> 00:30:32,400
we're…

723
00:30:32,790 --> 00:30:34,120
like we're the same age.

724
00:30:35,420 --> 00:30:36,740
That's why

725
00:30:36,790 --> 00:30:38,490
I like making movies.

726
00:30:38,940 --> 00:30:41,220
It's about the warmth
and coldness of people,

727
00:30:41,220 --> 00:30:43,420
the joy, anger, sorrow, and happiness.

728
00:30:43,460 --> 00:30:45,010
Once I get the loan,

729
00:30:45,090 --> 00:30:46,150
I'll tell my master

730
00:30:46,330 --> 00:30:47,140
about this.

731
00:30:47,920 --> 00:30:50,220
No, don't tell him.

732
00:30:50,400 --> 00:30:51,640
We'll wait until shooting starts

733
