Um, the doctor...

754
00:32:32,070 --> 00:32:33,270
The doctor...

755
00:32:33,790 --> 00:32:34,590
said...

756
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:37,140
He said that your cochlea

757
00:32:37,740 --> 00:32:39,590
will be functional

758
00:32:39,850 --> 00:32:40,810
