759
00:32:41,700 --> 00:32:42,850
In one month.

760
00:32:49,700 --> 00:32:51,050
Have some.

761
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:53,330
A little closer.

762
00:33:02,240 --> 00:33:04,100
Are you really going to get a loan?

763
00:33:04,720 --> 00:33:05,680
Let me remind you.

764
00:33:05,680 --> 00:33:07,280
We're just ordinary people.

765
00:33:08,600 --> 00:33:10,580
There are risks involved in this.

766
00:33:09,710 --> 00:33:13,320
[Seasons Change Hostel]
[Inside the Yard]

767
