783
00:33:44,200 --> 00:33:45,730
Why are you so negative now?

784
00:33:46,530 --> 00:33:47,390
What happened?

785
00:33:48,290 --> 00:33:48,950
Nothing.

786
00:33:48,980 --> 00:33:49,940
Don't give me that.

787
00:33:49,940 --> 00:33:50,670
Just tell me.

788
00:33:54,290 --> 00:33:55,270
I just feel like

789
