803
00:34:21,480 --> 00:34:22,690
That's your business.

804
00:34:22,690 --> 00:34:23,650
It is my business.

805
00:34:23,650 --> 00:34:25,250
But what can I express to her?

806
00:34:25,400 --> 00:34:26,460
What can I give her?

807
00:34:27,030 --> 00:34:28,230
Didn't you wait until

808
00:34:28,230 --> 00:34:29,340
