810
00:34:31,260 --> 00:34:32,730
That has nothing to do with money.

811
00:34:32,730 --> 00:34:34,090
How does it not?

812
00:34:34,130 --> 00:34:35,170
If you and Jun

813
00:34:35,210 --> 00:34:36,780
