817
00:34:46,510 --> 00:34:47,630
then go earn it.

818
00:34:48,090 --> 00:34:50,280
Don't worry about
if you can actually make it.

819
00:34:50,280 --> 00:34:50,940
At least it's better

820
00:34:50,940 --> 00:34:53,070
than just sitting here overthinking.

821
00:34:56,590 --> 00:34:57,050
Come on.

822
00:34:57,780 --> 00:34:58,510
To you.

823
00:34:58,020 --> 00:35:06,050
[Seasons Change Hostel]
[Inside the Yard]

824
00:34:58,940 --> 00:34:59,360
Right?

825
00:35:00,940 --> 00:35:03,270
Sorry for interrupting your good moment.

826
00:35:05,090 --> 00:35:06,420
