831
00:35:20,570 --> 00:35:22,500
-Look. I'll show you.
-Go ahead. Show me.

832
00:35:22,500 --> 00:35:23,000
Look.

833
00:35:24,810 --> 00:35:27,010
[Seasons Change Hostel]
[Inside the Yard]

834
00:35:25,940 --> 00:35:26,670
Not bad, huh?

835
00:35:27,890 --> 00:35:35,020
[Destined to Meet Co., Ltd.,]

836
00:35:28,730 --> 00:35:30,460
Right, they have 50

837
00:35:30,580 --> 00:35:32,730
JC 10 high-speed sewing machines.

838
00:35:33,570 --> 00:35:34,860
It's a sewing machine,

839
00:35:35,550 --> 00:35:37,880
