840
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:38,730
Okay, I'll wait for your call.

841
00:35:38,730 --> 00:35:40,460
They're in a hurry to sell them.

842
00:35:41,110 --> 00:35:42,070
Okay, okay.

843
00:35:42,380 --> 00:35:43,230
Hurry up.

844
00:35:44,320 --> 00:35:45,380
Exactly 2 minutes.

845
00:35:45,500 --> 00:35:46,560
I saved more money.

846
00:35:46,730 --> 00:35:47,010
Wait.

847
00:35:47,010 --> 00:35:47,670
Wait, wait.

848
00:35:48,340 --> 00:35:49,590
Tell me what's going on.

849
00:35:49,590 --> 00:35:51,650
Not playing your saxophone anymore?

850
00:35:52,130 --> 00:35:53,130
Didn't you say

851
00:35:54,050 --> 00:35:57,230
