852
00:35:57,380 --> 00:35:59,310
So you've thought of Mr. Lucky now?

853
00:36:00,230 --> 00:36:01,710
What do you want to do?

854
00:36:02,780 --> 00:36:03,860
How about you work with me fir—

855
