In ancient times,

873
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:30,090
it was a very noble profession.

874
00:36:30,320 --> 00:36:31,210
It was called a matchmaker.

875
00:36:31,210 --> 00:36:32,360
The one with a mole here,

876
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:33,890
playing matchmaker,

877
00:36:33,940 --> 00:36:35,050
introducing people to each other.

878
00:36:35,050 --> 00:36:36,340
What about modern times?

879
00:36:36,340 --> 00:36:37,630
See, you're not listening.

880
00:36:37,630 --> 00:36:38,360
Didn't I just say?

881
00:36:38,360 --> 00:36:39,710
It's brokering.

882
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:40,840
It's about information gaps.

883
00:36:40,840 --> 00:36:41,170
I'm telling you,

884
00:36:41,170 --> 00:36:42,210
you gotta be hardworking

885
00:36:42,210 --> 00:36:42,960
and smart to do this.

886
00:36:42,960 --> 00:36:43,500
I can do that.

887
00:36:43,500 --> 00:36:44,960
Collect info everywhere,

888
00:36:45,090 --> 00:36:46,220
perk up your ears,

889
00:36:46,340 --> 00:36:47,480
and take in every word.

890
00:36:47,480 --> 00:36:48,710
You need to keep your eyes wide open.

891
00:36:48,710 --> 00:36:49,800
Every strand of your hair must stand up

892
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:50,800
like an antenna,

893
00:36:50,820 --> 00:36:52,880
collecting all money-making news.

894
00:36:52,960 --> 00:36:54,460
As long as I can drive a Benz,

895
00:36:54,460 --> 00:36:55,150
you can stick

896
00:36:55,150 --> 00:36:56,610
antennas all over my head.

897
00:36:56,760 --> 00:36:57,630
You wish.

898
00:36:57,690 --> 00:36:58,460
A Benz?

899
00:36:58,530 --> 00:37:00,060
Do you see me driving a Benz?

900
00:37:01,730 --> 00:37:02,440
You should pray first.

901
00:37:02,440 --> 00:37:03,670
Do you know how to pray?

902
00:37:03,670 --> 00:37:04,320
Let me teach you how.

903
00:37:04,280 --> 00:37:12,990
[Honesty and Mutual Success]

904
00:37:04,320 --> 00:37:05,340
There's a standard process for doing this.

905
00:37:05,340 --> 00:37:05,820
Kneel.

906
00:37:07,210 --> 00:37:07,730
That's why I say

907
00:37:07,730 --> 00:37:08,790
you're a lucky guy.

908
00:37:08,940 --> 00:37:10,110
There happens to be
a Hong Kong businessman recently

909
00:37:10,110 --> 00:37:11,460
looking to acquire a mainland factory.

910
00:37:11,460 --> 00:37:12,540
We hit the jackpot.

911
00:37:15,500 --> 00:37:16,070
Ma.

912
00:37:17,070 --> 00:37:19,020
To be honest with you,

913
00:37:19,550 --> 00:37:20,860
this private factory

914
00:37:20,940 --> 00:37:22,370
is my lifeblood.

915
00:37:23,610 --> 00:37:25,890
If it weren't for the severe losses,

916
00:37:27,320 --> 00:37:28,480
I really don't want to

917
00:37:28,480 --> 00:37:29,800
sell it.

918
00:37:31,730 --> 00:37:32,730
Director, you...

919
00:37:34,090 --> 00:37:35,690
Are you going to regret this?

920
00:37:36,280 --> 00:37:37,420
It's such a big factory,

921
00:37:37,420 --> 00:37:39,680
and it has been running for so many years.

922
00:37:40,010 --> 00:37:42,010
You really need to think it through.

923
00:37:42,070 --> 00:37:42,880
Yeah.

924
00:37:42,980 --> 00:37:44,880
What's there to think about?

925
00:37:45,340 --> 00:37:46,570
I've already arranged everything.

926
00:37:46,570 --> 00:37:47,460
That Hong Kong businessman

927
00:37:47,460 --> 00:37:50,060
will fly over with the money
in a couple of days.

928
00:37:52,460 --> 00:37:54,320
I hate to sell it, but what can I do?

929
00:37:55,000 --> 00:37:56,320
Everyone in the factory

930
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:57,720
is waiting to be fed.

931
00:37:58,090 --> 00:37:59,290
If I don't sell it now,

932
00:38:00,300 --> 00:38:01,700
we really won't survive.

933
00:38:02,820 --> 00:38:05,550
Director, you really understand
the situation.

934
00:38:09,760 --> 00:38:11,170
Come on, move forward.

935
00:38:11,460 --> 00:38:12,740
Come.

936
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:14,070
Move forward.

937
00:38:14,230 --> 00:38:16,650
Okay, stop. Alright.

938
00:38:18,650 --> 00:38:20,000
Mr. Huang, it must have been a long trip.

939
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:20,910
Not at all.

940
00:38:21,070 --> 00:38:22,460
As long as there's money to be made,

941
00:38:22,460 --> 00:38:23,880
any hard work is worth it.

942
00:38:24,590 --> 00:38:25,610
Yes, yes.

943
00:38:25,650 --> 00:38:25,960
Right?

944
00:38:25,960 --> 00:38:27,010
Since we're doing business together,

945
00:38:27,010 --> 00:38:28,550
we are family, right?

946
00:38:30,760 --> 00:38:31,460
I'm sorry.

947
00:38:31,490 --> 00:38:33,120
I'm a clean freak.

948
00:38:33,340 --> 00:38:34,600
I understand.

949
00:38:35,500 --> 00:38:36,550
Businessmen probably

950
00:38:36,550 --> 00:38:38,250
all have their own quirks, right?

951
00:38:38,250 --> 00:38:39,580
That factory director—

952
00:38:39,730 --> 00:38:40,760
will he be difficult to deal with?

953
00:38:40,760 --> 00:38:42,440
Do we need to bribe him?

954
00:38:42,980 --> 00:38:44,350
We don't need to see him today,

955
00:38:44,350 --> 00:38:45,110
and no need for bribes either.

956
00:38:45,110 --> 00:38:45,760
For these little things,

957
00:38:45,760 --> 00:38:46,960
just leave them to me.

958
00:38:47,380 --> 00:38:48,380
Now that you're here,

959
00:38:48,380 --> 00:38:50,260
just eat well, drink well,

960
00:38:50,340 --> 00:38:52,140
and make yourself comfortable.

961
00:38:52,890 --> 00:38:54,490
What do you want to eat today?

962
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:56,980
I heard Beijing has a lot of good food.

963
00:38:57,460 --> 00:38:58,550
There's plenty.

964
00:38:58,800 --> 00:38:59,380
Sir,

965
00:38:59,530 --> 00:39:00,670
park the car in that parking lot.

966
00:39:00,670 --> 00:39:02,000
We'll leave after eating.

967
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:03,570
I'll take him to the hotel later.

968
00:39:03,570 --> 00:39:04,460
Let's go.

969
00:39:05,370 --> 00:39:07,770
[Wenzhou City Central Hospital]

970
00:39:08,010 --> 00:39:08,800
Dr. Zhang,

971
00:39:09,070 --> 00:39:10,780
I am Zhuang Meiqin's husband.

972
00:39:11,050 --> 00:39:12,710
I know you. Please take a seat.

973
00:39:16,460 --> 00:39:17,860
The test results are out.

974
00:39:18,110 --> 00:39:18,640
[Test Report]

975
00:39:18,660 --> 00:39:19,430
[CT Scan Report]

976
00:39:20,130 --> 00:39:21,130
It's lung cancer.

977
00:39:23,630 --> 00:39:25,150
The results came out a bit late.

978
00:39:25,150 --> 00:39:27,300
It is already in the middle
to late stages.

979
00:39:27,300 --> 00:39:28,880
But fortunately, the cancerous area

980
00:39:28,880 --> 00:39:29,810
isn't too large.

981
00:39:31,150 --> 00:39:31,920
The most important thing now

982
00:39:31,920 --> 00:39:34,320
is to arrange a surgery
as soon as possible.

983
00:39:34,500 --> 00:39:35,510
I'll have her do
some preoperative preparations

984
00:39:35,510 --> 00:39:36,820
over the next few days,

985
00:39:38,050 --> 00:39:40,180
and then we will schedule the surgery.

986
00:39:40,630 --> 00:39:41,900
Will she be okay?

987
00:39:43,900 --> 00:39:45,430
We can't be sure about that,

988
00:39:46,670 --> 00:39:48,030
but we will do our best.

989
00:39:51,900 --> 00:39:53,240
[Test Report]

990
00:39:53,270 --> 00:39:55,280
[They are consistent with the features
of peripherally-located lung cancer.]

991
00:40:07,650 --> 00:40:09,990
[Seasons Change Hostel]

992
00:40:10,020 --> 00:40:15,330
[Receipt from
Peking Union Medical College Hospital]

993
00:40:30,100 --> 00:40:31,630
Why are you looking at this?

994
00:40:32,670 --> 00:40:36,730
You lied to me.

995
00:40:40,050 --> 00:40:43,380
I didn't lie to you.

996
00:40:44,010 --> 00:40:45,550
This is so expensive.

997
00:40:46,650 --> 00:40:47,670
What?

998
00:40:50,190 --> 00:40:53,780
Where did you get the money?
You borrowed it?

999
00:40:57,590 --> 00:40:59,250
Where did the money come from?

1000
00:41:05,650 --> 00:41:09,590
We have to thank Ranran

1001
00:41:10,590 --> 00:41:14,690
for making this surgery possible.

1002
00:41:17,050 --> 00:41:17,880
Ranran?

1003
00:41:19,980 --> 00:41:21,130
I can...

1004
00:41:21,760 --> 00:41:24,960
pay this money back.

1005
00:41:26,110 --> 00:41:28,530
Trust me.

1006
00:41:29,170 --> 00:41:30,840
We'll pay it back together.

1007
00:41:33,440 --> 00:41:36,420
You've suffered a lot.

1008
00:41:36,630 --> 00:41:37,550
It's nothing.

1009
00:41:47,730 --> 00:41:48,390
Gentlemen.

1010
00:41:48,840 --> 00:41:50,000
Today we are formally holding

1011
00:41:50,000 --> 00:41:51,130
a negotiation meeting

1012
00:41:51,130 --> 00:41:53,970
on foreign investment partnership.

1013
00:41:52,120 --> 00:42:00,490
[Negotiation Meeting
on Foreign Investment Partnership]

1014
00:41:54,460 --> 00:41:55,410
This meeting

1015
00:41:55,440 --> 00:41:56,190
is based on

1016
00:41:56,530 --> 00:41:58,660
principles of openness and equality,

1017
00:41:59,000 --> 00:42:01,350
aimed at addressing
the difficulties of our factory.

1018
00:42:01,350 --> 00:42:02,440
We've invited Mr. Huang,

1019
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:04,060
who came all the way

1020
00:42:04,110 --> 00:42:04,970
from Hong Kong,

1021
00:42:05,000 --> 00:42:05,530
as well as

1022
00:42:05,570 --> 00:42:06,970
Mr. Zhu and Mr. Li,

1023
00:42:07,090 --> 00:42:08,950
who are interested in investing.

1024
00:42:09,190 --> 00:42:10,970
Everyone is encouraged

1025
00:42:11,190 --> 00:42:12,450
to be honest, sincere,

1026
00:42:17,550 --> 00:42:18,630
and speak freely.

1027
00:42:23,150 --> 00:42:23,790
We are

1028
00:42:23,960 --> 00:42:25,290
all doing big business.

1029
00:42:25,530 --> 00:42:28,160
What matters is investment versus return.

1030
00:42:28,400 --> 00:42:30,340
Spending a little money
to make a big profit—

1031
00:42:30,340 --> 00:42:31,400
that's a good deal.

1032
00:42:32,280 --> 00:42:32,780
We think

1033
00:42:32,820 --> 00:42:34,570
the current purchase price

1034
00:42:34,800 --> 00:42:35,740
is reasonable,

1035
00:42:36,010 --> 00:42:38,150
and the factory's performance is stable,

1036
00:42:38,150 --> 00:42:39,480
so we're willing to bid.

1037
00:42:42,880 --> 00:42:43,610
Director.

1038
00:42:44,710 --> 00:42:47,420
I've actually inspected

1039
00:42:47,530 --> 00:42:50,220
many similar-sized companies

1040
00:42:50,530 --> 00:42:52,280
in the mainland.

1041
00:42:53,900 --> 00:42:55,520
Your price today

1042
00:42:55,710 --> 00:42:56,710
is not low.
